title: Weekly sports quiz: Whose overhead kick helped Scotland reach World Cup?
text:
So much has happened over the past seven days, including football World Cup qualifiers, netball grudge matches and build-up to the first Ashes Test.

About 11% of quizzers got full marks in last week's edition. Will you make the grade this week?
summary: How much attention have you paid to what's been happening in the world of sport over the past seven days?
